## ğŸ“Œ Project Overview

This project is completed as part of the **AI & ML Internship Program**.
The objective of this task is to perform **unsupervised learning** using the **K-Means Clustering algorithm** to discover patterns and group similar data points without labeled outputs.

The project demonstrates dataset visualization, optimal cluster selection, clustering evaluation, and interpretation of results.

